$ Oracle: polymorphic table functions (PTF)

{ Requirements for a polymorphic table function

  A *package specification* that has a `describe` function
  
  Optionally, this package specification also comes with one or more of the functions/procedures
    • `open`
    • `fetch_rows`
    • `close`

  A *ptf package body*.

  A *PTF function* to reference the package.
  -
  This *PTF function* can be a stand alone function or in the same package where also the other functions are located.

}

